net.dv8tion.jda.core.entities

Interface VoiceChannel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AudioChannel, Channel, java.lang.Comparable<VoiceChannel>, ISnowflake
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    VoiceChannelImpl

    public interface VoiceChannel
extends Channel, AudioChannel, java.lang.Comparable<VoiceChannel>
    Represents a Discord Voice Channel. A specification of AudioChannel.
    As a VoiceChannel has no extra functionality as its Channel parent, this interface is empty. This interface only exists to distinct Channels into VoiceChannels and TextChannels.

      • getBitrate

        int getBitrate()
        The audio bitrate of the voice audio that is transmitted in this channel. While higher bitrates can be sent to this channel, it will be scaled down by the client.
